skdetail:

Invocation Name: princeton calendar
des: This skill tells you all academic events and deadlines on a given date for Princeton University starting from September 9th, 2015. Simply ask for events on a date or a period of time such as this month or year.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
